OL,3,CGo-ahead given to clean-up dumped
OL,4,Cwaste at Hoad's Wood ancient woodland
OL,6,FThe Secretary of State Steve Barclay
OL,7,Fhas ordered that the Environment
OL,8,FAgency must clear tonnes of waste from
OL,9,Fancient woodland in Kent.
OL,11,FConservationists say they are
OL,12,Fdelighted after the clean-up was
OL,13,Fapproved at a Site of Special
OL,14,FScientific Interest that lies buried
OL,15,Fbeneath a mountain of illegally dumped
OL,16,Fwaste.
OL,18,FOrganised criminals disposed of tonnes
OL,19,Fof processed rubbish at the wildlife
OL,20,Fhaven near Ashford.
