OL,6,FWildlife filmmaker and conservationist
OL,7,FRichard Taylor-Jones talks of the
OL,8,Ftriumph of today's decision
OL,10,FIn April, Kent Wildlife Trust, RSPB,
OL,11,FThe Woodland Trust, South East Rivers
OL,12,FTrust, CPRE Kent, the CLA and the
OL,13,FRescue Hoad's Wood campaign wrote to
OL,14,Fthe Secretary of State, Steve Barclay
OL,15,Fasking that he used his powers to
OL,16,Frelease emergency funds to begin an
OL,17,Furgent clean-up operation.
