OL,3,CGo-ahead given to clean-up dumped
OL,4,Cwaste at Hoad's Wood ancient woodland
OL,6,F"This marks a significant step forward
OL,7,Fin our efforts to restore the natural
OL,8,Fbeauty of this ancient bluebell
OL,9,Fwoodland.
OL,11,F"We eagerly anticipate the swift
OL,12,Fcompletion of the cleanup operation so
OL,13,Fthe recovery process can commence.
OL,14,FAdditionally, we also look forward to
OL,15,Fa comprehensive investigation into
OL,16,Flocal and national authorities'
OL,17,Finaction, which allowed this
OL,18,Fenvironmental catastrophe to occur,
OL,19,Fdespite our community's diligent
OL,20,Freporting.
